To begin, recall that we have some major principles when it come to define 
"intermediate" python.
一旦涉及到中级python，必须保持主要原则。
Two of them were that our code needs to be efficient and scale, and another 
was that others should be able to easily understand and use our code.
其中两条分别是：代码必须高效且模块化，其次须简单易懂，其他人也能快速上手。
These two principles come into contention when it comes to string operation.
这两条原则在使用string相关操作时就充满争议。
具体内容可看 string_contention.py